    question: '<p>Create a checkbox group with two checkboxes and larger clickable area</p>\n<pre><code class="language-html">&#x3C;tagA>\n &#x3C;legend>\n   Choose favorite meal\n &#x3C;/legend>\n   &#x3C;div>\n    &#x3C;tagB\n       type="tagC" id="soup"\n       name="meal" value="soup" tagD>\n    &#x3C;tagE\n       for="soup">Soup\n    &#x3C;/tagE>\n   &#x3C;/div>\n   &#x3C;div>\n    &#x3C;tagB\n       type="tagC" id="burgers"\n       name="meal" value="burgers">\n    &#x3C;tagE\n       for="burgers">Burgers\n    &#x3C;/tagE>\n   &#x3C;/div\n&#x3C;/tagA>\n</code></pre>\n<p>tagA: ???\ntagB: ???\ntagC: ???\ntagD: ???\ntagE: ???</p>\n',
